        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: add timeout to scp spawn to prevent hanging in sandbox media staging",
        "body": "Related: #98468\n\n## What Problem This Solves\n\n`scpFile()` spawns scp child process with no timeout — hung connection leaks process + Promise.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nAdd 30-second `SCP_TIMEOUT_MS` with `SIGKILL` and `settled` guard to prevent double-resolution.\n\n## User Impact\n\nPrevents hung SCP operations from leaking resources during remote sandbox staging.\n\n## Evidence\n\nSource verification (fix/scp-timeout branch):\n\n```\n$ grep -n \"SCP_TIMEOUT_MS\\|SIGKILL\\|settled\" stage-sandbox-media.ts\n24: const SCP_TIMEOUT_MS = 30_000;\n390: settled = true;\n391: child.kill(\"SIGKILL\");\n392: reject(new Error(`scp timed out after ${SCP_TIMEOUT_MS}ms`));\nSCP_TIMEOUT_MS=30000, settled guard + SIGKILL confirmed in source\n```\n\n- `stage-sandbox-media.scp-remote-path.test.ts`: 5/5 passed ✅",
        "branch": "fix/scp-timeout",
